<plot>Leo Gogarty marries Margaud Morgan after a whirlwind romance just before shipping out to war. When he returns he is surprised to discover not only that his bride is not what she led him to believe, but also that she expects a quick divorce. Both Mr. &amp; Mrs Gogarty must find their place with or without each other in a society still adjusting to peace.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?339289</url></doc>
